{"tid":453343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指藉上門追債強姦女街坊 無業漢被判無罪","createTime":"2017-10-31T05:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T06:11:51.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"740394ff32e3789c1d1f8561d9ca65fd14c7c2f3","tid":453343,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>被指藉上門追債強姦女街坊 無業漢被判無罪</strong><br />\n<br />\n35歲無業漢被指去年9月上門追債時，於女街坊家中將對方強姦對方，案件經審訊後，陪審團今早一致裁定無業漢罪名不成立，被告獲當庭釋放。<br />\n<br />\n被告李文傑（35歲）被控於去年9月28日在深水埗強姦X。他於警誡下表示當天上門追債，他與事主X均服食了毒品，及後兩人在沒有使用安全套下性交，他否認強姦X。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/4k0M6JM3D7tpC/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F4k0M6JM3D7tpC%2Fgiphy.gif&h=45915b17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"739e70fafef42181a5a795bb98fd3a39f9141d24","tid":453343,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:50:07.000Z","msg":"要射呀，吹咩"},{"pid":"0af0a39db97c2ea90045a5cd0cf7f8e8acb28934","tid":453343,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"係咪成班道姑道友嗰單？"},{"pid":"81ac61fe47d7fa40036369934f1dd049c224f831","tid":453343,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"兩人在沒有使用安全套下性交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f541653fab686cd31cfc12fcaacc4f2f695f2c4","tid":453343,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪成班道姑道友嗰單？</blockquote><br />\n強姦案事主求不要體內射精   被告回應：要射呀，吹咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439967/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439967/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e02865b44bef74077b4ce58e68c539f1f9b04b93","tid":453343,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"